STATE EX REL. JAMES
v.
PARK. 2017-1662 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 28, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On respondents' motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. On relator's motion to strike motion to dismiss and motion for default judgment. Motions denied as moot. On respondents' motion for leave to file amended motion to dismiss and proposed amended motion to dismiss. Motions denied as moot.
